review_title: Great value! Amazing device with epic chorma
reviews:
Camera was way better then what I was expecting, did all my tests on device on same day I got it. Device works (as a phone too) quality on calls are great and the performance is amazing and I know the battery is new but it appears to pretty heavy duty as it doesn't consume power as bad as I thought it might, But then again, how can you go wrong with a 4000mah battery on a power house like this beaut.
PS: The boxy style is pretty badass, I like it (but I have big hands)
Thank you RAZER for yet another great quality device.
